#. type: Title ==
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:52
#, no-wrap
msgid "Synopsis"
msgstr "概述"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:57
msgid ""
"While FreeBSD is popular as a server for its performance and stability, it is also suited for day-to-day use as a desktop.  With over {numports} applications "
"available as FreeBSD packages or ports, it is easy to build a customized desktop that runs a wide variety of desktop applications.  This chapter demonstrates how to "
"install numerous desktop applications, including web browsers, productivity software, document viewers, and financial software."
msgstr ""
"虽然 FreeBSD 常常因为其性能和稳定性而被作为服务器使用，但它也适合作为日常的桌面操作系统来使用。通过 FreeBSD 提供的 Packages 和 Ports，您可以获取超过 {numports} 个应"
"用程序，并轻松地建立起一个可以运行各种桌面应用程序的操作环境。本章将演示如何安装许多桌面应用程序，包括网络浏览器、生产力工具、文档浏览器和财务软件。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:61
msgid ""
"Users who prefer to install a pre-built desktop version of FreeBSD rather than configuring one from scratch should refer to https://ghostbsd.org[GhostBSD], https://"
"www.midnightbsd.org[MidnightBSD] or https://nomadbsd.org[NomadBSD]."
msgstr ""
"如果用户喜欢安装预先构建好的桌面版 FreeBSD，而不是从头开始配置，可以参考 https://ghostbsd.org[GhostBSD] 、 https://www.midnightbsd.org[MidnightBSD] 或 https://"
"nomadbsd.org[NomadBSD]。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:64
msgid "Readers of this chapter should know how to:"
msgstr "本章节的读者应该知道如何进行以下事项："

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:66
msgid "Install additional software using packages or ports as described in crossref:ports[ports,Installing Applications: Packages and Ports]."
msgstr "使用 第4章 安装应用程序：crossref:ports[ports,安装应用程序：软件包和 Ports] 中所述的 packages 和 ports 来安装额外的软件。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:67
msgid "Install X and a window manager as described in crossref:x11[x11,The X Window System]."
msgstr "依据 第5章 crossref:x11[x11,The X Window 系统] 中的指引，安装 X 和窗口管理器。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:69
msgid "For information on how to configure a multimedia environment, refer to crossref:multimedia[multimedia,Multimedia]."
msgstr "有关配置多媒体环境的信息，请参阅 第7章 crossref:multimedia[multimedia,多媒体]。"

#. type: Title ==
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:71
#, no-wrap
msgid "Browsers"
msgstr "浏览器"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:75
msgid ""
"FreeBSD does not come with a pre-installed web browser.  Instead, the https://www.FreeBSD.org/ports/[www] category of the Ports Collection contains many browsers "
"which can be installed as a package or compiled from the Ports Collection."
msgstr ""
"虽然 FreeBSD 并没有预装网络浏览器，但是 Ports Collection 的https://www.FreeBSD.org/ports/[www]类别中包含了许多浏览器，它们可以作为软件包来安装或者从 Ports "
"Collection 中编译安装。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:78
msgid ""
"The KDE and GNOME desktop environments include their own HTML browser.  Refer to crossref:x11[x11-wm,“Desktop Environments”] for more information on how to set up "
"these complete desktops."
msgstr "KDE 和 GNOME 桌面环境包含了它们自己的 HTML 浏览器，关于设置这些桌面的教程，请参考 crossref:x11[x11-wm,“桌面环境”]。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:80
msgid "Some lightweight browsers include package:www/dillo2[], package:www/links[], and package:www/w3m[]."
msgstr "您也可以使用一些轻量级的浏览器，比如 package:www/dillo2[], package:www/links[] 和 package:www/w3m[]。"

