#. type: Title ===
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:107
#, no-wrap
msgid "Firefox"
msgstr "Firefox"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:111
msgid ""
"Firefox is an open source browser that features a standards-compliant HTML display engine, tabbed browsing, popup blocking, extensions, improved security, and "
"more.  Firefox is based on the Mozilla codebase."
msgstr "Firefox 是一个以标准化 HTML 渲染引擎、多标签页浏览，弹窗拦截、可选扩展、更高的安全性等为特色的开源的浏览器。Firefox 由 Mozilla 的代码构建。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:113
msgid "To install the package of the latest release version of Firefox, type:"
msgstr "欲安装最新版本的 Firefox，请在终端输入："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:117
#, no-wrap
msgid "# pkg install firefox\n"
msgstr "# pkg install firefox\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:120
msgid "To instead install Firefox Extended Support Release (ESR) version, use:"
msgstr "欲安装 Firefox 长期支持版(即 Firefox ESR, Extended Support Release)，请使用："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:124
#, no-wrap
msgid "# pkg install firefox-esr\n"
msgstr "# pkg install firefox-esr\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:128
msgid ""
"The Ports Collection can instead be used to compile the desired version of Firefox from source code.  This example builds package:www/firefox[], where `firefox` can "
"be replaced with the ESR or localized version to install."
msgstr ""
"您也可以使用 Ports Collection 来编译安装您想要的 Firefox 版本，在这个实例中，我们将构建 www/firefox，其中，这里提到的 `firefox` 也可以是长期支持版或者其他本地化定制"
"的版本。"

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:133
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# cd /usr/ports/www/firefox\n"
"# make install clean\n"
msgstr ""
"# cd /usr/ports/www/firefox\n"
"# make install clean\n"

#. type: Title ===
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:135
#, no-wrap
msgid "Konqueror"
msgstr "Konqueror"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:140
msgid ""
"Konqueror is more than a web browser as it is also a file manager and a multimedia viewer.  Supports WebKit as well as its own KHTML.  WebKit is a rendering engine "
"used by many modern browsers including Chromium."
msgstr ""
"Konqueror 不仅仅是一个网页浏览器，它还是一个文件管理器和多媒体的查看器。Konqueror 支持 WebKit 和它自己的 KHTML 内核。其中，WebKit 是许多现代浏览器使用的渲染引擎，包"
"括Chromium。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:142
msgid "Konqueror can be installed as a package by typing:"
msgstr "欲使用 packages 来安装，请输入："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:146
#, no-wrap
msgid "# pkg install konqueror\n"
msgstr "# pkg install konqueror\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:149
msgid "To install from the Ports Collection:"
msgstr "欲从 Ports Collection 中编译安装，请输入："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:154
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# cd /usr/ports/x11-fm/konqueror/\n"
"# make install clean\n"
msgstr ""
"# cd /usr/ports/x11-fm/konqueror/\n"
"# make install clean\n"

#. type: Title ===
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:156
#, no-wrap
msgid "Chromium"
msgstr "Chromium"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:161
msgid ""
"Chromium is an open source browser project that aims to build a safer, faster, and more stable web browsing experience.  Chromium features tabbed browsing, popup "
"blocking, extensions, and much more.  Chromium is the open source project upon which the Google Chrome web browser is based."
msgstr ""
"Chromium 是一个开源的浏览器项目，旨在提供一个更加安全、快速、稳定的网络浏览体验，同时具有标签式浏览、弹出窗口拦截、浏览器扩展等功能，谷歌的 Chrome 浏览器就是基于这个"
"项目。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:163
msgid "Chromium can be installed as a package by typing:"
msgstr "欲使用 packages 来安装 Chromium，请输入："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:167
#, no-wrap
msgid "# pkg install chromium\n"
msgstr "# pkg install chromium\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:170
msgid "Alternatively, Chromium can be compiled from source using the Ports Collection:"
msgstr "您也可以从 Ports Collection 中编译安装 Chromium："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:175
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# cd /usr/ports/www/chromium\n"
"# make install clean\n"
msgstr ""
"# cd /usr/ports/www/chromium\n"
"# make install clean\n"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:180
msgid "The executable for Chromium is [.filename]#/usr/local/bin/chrome#, not [.filename]#/usr/local/bin/chromium#."
msgstr "Chromium 的可执行文件是 [.filename]#/usr/local/bin/chrome#，而不是 [.filename]#/usr/local/bin/chromium#。"

#. type: Title ==
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:183
#, no-wrap
msgid "Productivity"
msgstr "生产力工具"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:188
msgid ""
"When it comes to productivity, users often look for an office suite or an easy-to-use word processor.  While some <<x11-wm,desktop environments>> like KDE provide "
"an office suite, there is no default productivity package.  Several office suites and graphical word processors are available for FreeBSD, regardless of the "
"installed window manager."
msgstr ""
"当提到生产力工具时，用户往往倾向于使用办公套件或者易于使用的文字处理软件。虽然有些 <<x11-wm,desktop environments>> 比如 KDE，他会提供一个默认的办公套件，但是 "
"FreeBSD 并没有提供默认的生产力工具包，您需要自己安装想要的办公套件和其他图形化的文字处理程序。FreeBSD 提供的生产力工具与您安装的窗口管理器或桌面的类型无关。"

