#. type: Title ===
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:225
#, no-wrap
msgid "Calligra"
msgstr "Calligra"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:230
msgid ""
"The KDE desktop environment includes an office suite which can be installed separately from KDE.  Calligra includes standard components that can be found in other "
"office suites.  Words is the word processor, Sheets is the spreadsheet program, Stage manages slide presentations, and Karbon is used to draw graphical documents."
msgstr ""
"KDE 桌面环境包含了一个可以被单独安装的办公套件，即 Calligra。Calligra 包含了在其他办公套件中可以找到的标准组件，其中，Words 是文字处理器，Sheets 是电子表格程序，"
"Stage 是幻灯片演示程序，Karbon 可用于绘制图形文档。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:233
msgid "In FreeBSD, package:editors/calligra[] can be installed as a package or a port.  To install the package:"
msgstr "在 FreeBSD 中，package:editors/calligra[] 能通过 package 或 port 来安装。欲使用 package 来安装，请使用："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:237
#, no-wrap
msgid "# pkg install calligra\n"
msgstr "# pkg install calligra\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:240
msgid "If the package is not available, use the Ports Collection instead:"
msgstr "如果 package 暂时不能使用，您也可以使用 ports 来安装："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:245
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# cd /usr/ports/editors/calligra\n"
"# make install clean\n"
msgstr ""
"# cd /usr/ports/editors/calligra\n"
"# make install clean\n"

#. type: Title ===
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:247
#, no-wrap
msgid "AbiWord"
msgstr "AbiWord"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:251
msgid "AbiWord is a free word processing program similar in look and feel to Microsoft(R) Word.  It is fast, contains many features, and is user-friendly."
msgstr "AbiWord 是一个免费的文字处理程序，在外观和感觉上与 Microsoft(R) Word 相似。它速度很快，包含许多功能，而且对用户很友好。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:253
msgid "AbiWord can import or export many file formats, including some proprietary ones like Microsoft(R) [.filename]#.rtf#."
msgstr "AbiWord 可以导入或导出许多文件格式，包括一些专有格式，如 Microsoft(R) [.filename]#.rtf#。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:255
msgid "To install the AbiWord package:"
msgstr "欲通过 package 安装 AbiWord，请使用："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:259
#, no-wrap
msgid "# pkg install abiword\n"
msgstr "# pkg install abiword\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:262
msgid "If the package is not available, it can be compiled from the Ports Collection:"
msgstr "如果 package 暂时不能使用，您也可以使用 ports 来安装："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:267
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# cd /usr/ports/editors/abiword\n"
"# make install clean\n"
msgstr ""
"# cd /usr/ports/editors/abiword\n"
"# make install clean\n"

#. type: Title ===
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:269
#, no-wrap
msgid "The GIMP"
msgstr "GIMP"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:275
msgid ""
"For image authoring or picture retouching, The GIMP provides a sophisticated image manipulation program.  It can be used as a simple paint program or as a quality "
"photo retouching suite.  It supports a large number of plugins and features a scripting interface.  The GIMP can read and write a wide range of file formats and "
"supports interfaces with scanners and tablets."
msgstr ""
"针对图像创作和修饰，GIMP 提供了一个多功能的图像处理程序，它既可以作为一个简单的绘画程序，也可以作为一个复杂的、多功能的、高质量的图像修饰程序。Gimp 支持脚本接口和许"
"多插件，也能读取和保存为多种不同类型的文件格式，还支持扫描仪和手写板。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:277
msgid "To install the package:"
msgstr "欲通过二进制包安装请使用："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:281
#, no-wrap
msgid "# pkg install gimp\n"
msgstr "# pkg install gimp\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:284
msgid "Alternately, use the Ports Collection:"
msgstr "也可以使用 Ports Collection："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:289
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# cd /usr/ports/graphics/gimp\n"
"# make install clean\n"
msgstr ""
"# cd /usr/ports/graphics/gimp\n"
"# make install clean\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:292
msgid ""
"The graphics category (https://www.FreeBSD.org/ports/graphics/[freebsd.org/ports/graphics/]) of the Ports Collection contains several GIMP-related plugins, help "
"files, and user manuals."
msgstr "Ports Collection 的 图像类别(https://www.FreeBSD.org/ports/graphics/[freebsd.org/ports/graphics/]) 中包含了许多跟 GIMP 有关的插件、帮助文档和用户手册。"

#. type: Title ===
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:293
#, no-wrap
msgid "Apache OpenOffice"
msgstr "Apache OpenOffice"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:299
msgid ""
"Apache OpenOffice is an open source office suite which is developed under the wing of the Apache Software Foundation's Incubator.  It includes all of the "
"applications found in a complete office productivity suite: a word processor, spreadsheet, presentation manager, and drawing program.  Its user interface is similar "
"to other office suites, and it can import and export in various popular file formats.  It is available in a number of different languages and internationalization "
"has been extended to interfaces, spell checkers, and dictionaries."
msgstr ""
"Apache OpenOffice 是一个开源的办公套件，在 Apache 软件基金会的孵化器的支持下开发。它包括一个完整的办公生产力套件应包含的所有应用程序：一个文字处理器、电子表格处理"
"器、幻灯片管理器和绘图程序。它的用户界面与其他办公套件相似，并且可以导入和导出各种流行的文件格式。它有许多不同的语言版本，并且支持界面、拼写检查器和字典等的本地化。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:305
msgid ""
"The word processor of Apache OpenOffice uses a native XML file format for increased portability and flexibility.  The spreadsheet program features a macro language "
"which can be interfaced with external databases.  Apache OpenOffice is stable and runs natively on Windows(R), Solaris(TM), Linux(R), FreeBSD, and Mac OS(R) X.  "
"More information about Apache OpenOffice can be found at http://openoffice.org/[openoffice.org].  For FreeBSD specific information refer to http://porting."
"openoffice.org/freebsd/[porting.openoffice.org/freebsd/]."
msgstr ""
"Apache OpenOffice 的文字处理器使用 XML 文件格式来增加可移植性和灵活性。其电子表格程序具有一个宏处理程序，可以与外部数据库连接。Apache OpenOffice 可以在 Windows(R) , "
"Solaris(TM) , Linux(R), FreeBSD , 和 Mac OS(R) X 上运行。关于 Apache OpenOffice 的更多信息，可以参考 http://openoffice.org/[openoffice.org]。关于 FreeBSD 的具体信"
"息，请参考 http://porting.openoffice.org/freebsd/[porting.openoffice.org/freebsd/]。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:307
msgid "To install the Apache OpenOffice package:"
msgstr "欲通过 package 安装 Apache OpenOffice，请使用："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:311
#, no-wrap
msgid "# pkg install apache-openoffice\n"
msgstr "# pkg install apache-openoffice\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:314
msgid "Once the package is installed, type the following command to launch Apache OpenOffice:"
msgstr "当上述安装过程完成后，您可以使用如下命令来启动 Apache OpenOffice:"

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:318
#, no-wrap
msgid "% openoffice-X.Y.Z\n"
msgstr "% openoffice-X.Y.Z\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:322
msgid ""
"where _X.Y.Z_ is the version number of the installed version of Apache OpenOffice.  The first time Apache OpenOffice launches, some questions will be asked and a [."
"filename]#.openoffice.org# folder will be created in the user's home directory."
msgstr ""
"注意，上述命令中的 _X.Y.Z_ 是指您安装的 Apache OpenOffice 的具体版本。当您第一次启动 Apache OpenOffice后，它会询问您几个问题，并且在用户主目录下创建一个名为 [."
"filename]#.openoffice.org# 的文件夹。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:325
msgid ""
"If the desired Apache OpenOffice package is not available, compiling the port is still an option.  However, this requires a lot of disk space and a fairly long time "
"to compile:"
msgstr ""
"如果您没法直接获取想要版本的 Apache OpenOffice，您可以考虑使用 port 来编译安装。不过，这种方法需要消耗非常多的磁盘空间和很长的时间来完成整个编译过程。命令如下："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:330
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# cd /usr/ports/editors/openoffice-4\n"
"# make install clean\n"
msgstr ""
"# cd /usr/ports/editors/openoffice-4\n"
"# make install clean\n"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:335
msgid "To build a localized version, replace the previous command with:"
msgstr "如果您想要构建一个本地化的版本，请用以下命令替代上述的 make 命令："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:339
#, no-wrap
msgid "# make LOCALIZED_LANG=your_language install clean\n"
msgstr "# make LOCALIZED_LANG=your_language install clean\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:343
msgid ""
"Replace _your_language_ with the correct language ISO-code.  A list of supported language codes is available in [.filename]#files/Makefile.localized#, located in "
"the port's directory."
msgstr "请使用正确的 ISO 语言代码来替代上述指令中的 _您的语言_。其中，在 ports 的目录 [.filename]#files/Makefile.localized# 中，您可以找到支持的语言的代码 。"

#. type: Title ===
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:345
#, no-wrap
msgid "LibreOffice"
msgstr "LibreOffice"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:351
msgid ""
"LibreOffice is a free software office suite developed by http://www.documentfoundation.org/[documentfoundation.org].  It is compatible with other major office "
"suites and available on a variety of platforms.  It is a rebranded fork of Apache OpenOffice and includes applications found in a complete office productivity "
"suite: a word processor, spreadsheet, presentation manager, drawing program, database management program, and a tool for creating and editing mathematical formulæ.  "
"It is available in a number of different languages and internationalization has been extended to interfaces, spell checkers, and dictionaries."
msgstr ""
"LibreOffice 是一个由 http://www.documentfoundation.org/[documentfoundation.org] 开发的免费办公软件套件。它与其他的主流办公套件相兼容，支持多种平台。它是 Apache "
"OpenOffice 的一个重命名分叉，包括一个完整的办公生产力套件中所应含有的应用程序：一个文字处理器、电子表格、幻灯片管理器绘图程序、数据库管理程序，以及一个用于创建和编辑"
"数学公式的工具。它有许多不同的语言版本，并且支持界面、拼写检查器和字典等的本地化。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:356
msgid ""
"The word processor of LibreOffice uses a native XML file format for increased portability and flexibility.  The spreadsheet program features a macro language which "
"can be interfaced with external databases.  LibreOffice is stable and runs natively on Windows(R), Linux(R), FreeBSD, and Mac OS(R) X.  More information about "
"LibreOffice can be found at http://www.libreoffice.org/[libreoffice.org]."
msgstr ""
"LibreOffice 的文字处理器使用 XML 文件格式来增加可移植性和灵活性。其电子表格程序具有一个宏处理程序，可以与外部数据库连接。LibreOffice 可以在 Windows(R) , "
"Solaris(TM) , Linux(R), FreeBSD , 和 Mac OS(R) X 上运行。关于 LibreOffice 的更多信息，可以参考 http://www.libreoffice.org/[libreoffice.org] 。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:358
msgid "To install the English version of the LibreOffice package:"
msgstr "欲安装英文版的 LibreOffice，请执行："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:362
#, no-wrap
msgid "# pkg install libreoffice\n"
msgstr "# pkg install libreoffice\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:366
msgid ""
"The editors category (https://www.FreeBSD.org/ports/editors/[freebsd.org/ports/editors/]) of the Ports Collection contains several localizations for LibreOffice.  "
"When installing a localized package, replace `libreoffice` with the name of the localized package."
msgstr ""
"在 Ports Collection 的编辑器类别 (https://www.FreeBSD.org/ports/editors/[freebsd.org/ports/editors/]) 中包含了许多 LibreOffice 的本地化版本，若您打算安装一个本地化的"
"版本，请将上述命令中的 `libreoffice` 替换为本地化版本软件包的具体名称。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:368
msgid "Once the package is installed, type the following command to run LibreOffice:"
msgstr "当上述安装过程完成后，您可以执行如下指令来启动 LibreOffice："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:372
#, no-wrap
msgid "% libreoffice\n"
msgstr "% libreoffice\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:375
msgid "During the first launch, some questions will be asked and a [.filename]#.libreoffice# folder will be created in the user's home directory."
msgstr "在启动过程中，LibreOffice 将会问您几个问题，并在用户主目录下创建一个名叫 [.filename]#.libreoffice# 的目录。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:379
msgid ""
"If the desired LibreOffice package is not available, compiling the port is still an option.  However, this requires a lot of disk space and a fairly long time to "
"compile.  This example compiles the English version:"
msgstr ""
"如果您没法直接获取想要版本的 LibreOffice，您可以考虑使用 port 来编译安装。不过，这种方法需要消耗非常多的磁盘空间和很长的时间来完成整个编译过程。编译安装英文版 "
"LibreOffice 的命令如下："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:384
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# cd /usr/ports/editors/libreoffice\n"
"# make install clean\n"
msgstr ""
"# cd /usr/ports/editors/libreoffice\n"
"# make install clean\n"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:390
msgid ""
"To build a localized version, `cd` into the port directory of the desired language.  Supported languages can be found in the editors category (https://www.FreeBSD."
"org/ports/editors/[freebsd.org/ports/editors/]) of the Ports Collection."
msgstr ""
"欲构建本地化版本的 LibreOffice，请先使用 `cd` 进入您想要的语言版本所对应的 port 目录。您可以在 Port Collection 的 编辑器类别 (https://www.FreeBSD.org/ports/editors/"
"[freebsd.org/ports/editors/]) 中找到支持的语言。"

