#. type: Title ===
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:432
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xpdf"
msgstr "Xpdf"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:436
msgid ""
"For users that prefer a small FreeBSD PDF viewer, Xpdf provides a light-weight and efficient viewer which requires few resources.  It uses the standard X fonts and "
"does not require any additional toolkits."
msgstr "对于那些更喜欢小型 FreeBSD PDF 查看器的用户，Xpdf 提供了一个轻量级和高效率的查看器。Xpdf 使用标准的 X 字体，且不需要任何额外工具。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:438
msgid "To install the Xpdf package:"
msgstr "欲通过二进制包来安装 Xpdf，请执行："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:442
#, no-wrap
msgid "# pkg install xpdf\n"
msgstr "# pkg install xpdf\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:445 content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:491 content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:589
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:611 content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:633
msgid "If the package is not available, use the Ports Collection:"
msgstr "如果二进制包暂时不能使用，您也可以使用 ports 来安装："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:450
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# cd /usr/ports/graphics/xpdf\n"
"# make install clean\n"
msgstr ""
"# cd /usr/ports/graphics/xpdf\n"
"# make install clean\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:453
msgid "Once the installation is complete, launch `xpdf` and use the right mouse button to activate the menu."
msgstr "当安装结束后，您可以执行 `xpdf` 来启动，并使用鼠标右键来显示操作菜单。"

#. type: Title ===
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:454
#, no-wrap
msgid "gv"
msgstr "gv"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:460
msgid ""
"gv is a PostScript(R) and PDF viewer.  It is based on ghostview, but has a nicer look as it is based on the Xaw3d widget toolkit.  gv has many configurable "
"features, such as orientation, paper size, scale, and anti-aliasing.  Almost any operation can be performed with either the keyboard or the mouse."
msgstr ""
"gv 是一个 PostScript(R) 和 PDF 查看器，它基于 ghostview ，但是由于 gv 还使用了基于 Xaw3d 的工具，它还拥有更好的界面。gv 拥有很多可以配置的特色功能，比如调整页面方"
"向、纸张大小、比例和抗锯齿等，几乎任何操作都可以用键盘或鼠标来完成。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:462
msgid "To install gv as a package:"
msgstr "欲通过二进制包来安装gv，请执行："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:466
#, no-wrap
msgid "# pkg install gv\n"
msgstr "# pkg install gv\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:469 content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:511 content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:531
msgid "If a package is unavailable, use the Ports Collection:"
msgstr "如果二进制包暂时不能使用，您也可以使用 Ports 来安装："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:474
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# cd /usr/ports/print/gv\n"
"# make install clean\n"
msgstr ""
"# cd /usr/ports/print/gv\n"
"# make install clean\n"

#. type: Title ===
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:476
#, no-wrap
msgid "Geeqie"
msgstr "Geeqie"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:482
msgid ""
"Geeqie is a fork from the unmaintained GQView project, in an effort to move development forward and integrate the existing patches.  Geeqie is an image manager "
"which supports viewing a file with a single click, launching an external editor, and thumbnail previews.  It also features a slideshow mode and some basic file "
"operations, making it easy to manage image collections and to find duplicate files.  Geeqie supports full screen viewing and internationalization."
msgstr ""
"Geeqie 是停止维护的 GQView 的 fork 版本，目的是推进开发，并整合现有的补丁。Geeqie 是一个额图像管理器，支持单击查看文件、启动外部编辑器以及略缩图预览，它还具有幻灯面"
"模式和一些基本的文件操作功能，使其能够轻松地管理图片集和查找重复的文件。Geeqie 支持全屏浏览和本地化。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:484
msgid "To install the Geeqie package:"
msgstr "欲通过二进制包来安装 Geeqie，请执行："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:488
#, no-wrap
msgid "# pkg install geeqie\n"
msgstr "# pkg install geeqie\n"

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:496
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# cd /usr/ports/graphics/geeqie\n"
"# make install clean\n"
msgstr ""
"# cd /usr/ports/graphics/geeqie\n"
"# make install clean\n"

#. type: Title ===
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:498
#, no-wrap
msgid "ePDFView"
msgstr "ePDFView"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:502
msgid ""
"ePDFView is a lightweight `PDF` document viewer that only uses the Gtk+ and Poppler libraries.  It is currently under development, but already opens most `PDF` "
"files (even encrypted), save copies of documents, and has support for printing using CUPS."
msgstr ""
"ePDFView 是一个只使用 GTK+ 和 Poppler 的库的轻量级的 pdf 查看器。虽然目前其仍在积极开发中，但是已经能够打开绝大多数 pdf 文件（甚至是加密的）、保存文件的复制件，并且"
"能够支持用 CUPS 来打印。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:504
msgid "To install ePDFView as a package:"
msgstr "欲通过二进制包来安装 ePDFView，请执行："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:508
#, no-wrap
msgid "# pkg install epdfview\n"
msgstr "# pkg install epdfview\n"

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:516
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# cd /usr/ports/graphics/epdfview\n"
"# make install clean\n"
msgstr ""
"# cd /usr/ports/graphics/epdfview\n"
"# make install clean\n"

#. type: Title ===
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:518
#, no-wrap
msgid "Okular"
msgstr "Okular"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:522
msgid "Okular is a universal document viewer based on KPDF for KDE.  It can open many document formats, including `PDF`, PostScript(R), DjVu, `CHM`, `XPS`, and ePub."
msgstr "Okular 是一个基于 KDE 的 KPDF 的通用文件查看器，能打开多种文件格式，包括 `PDF` 、PostScript(R)、DjVu、`CHM` 、`XPS` 和 ePub。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:524
msgid "To install Okular as a package:"
msgstr "欲通过二进制包来安装 ePDFView，请执行："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:528
#, no-wrap
msgid "# pkg install okular\n"
msgstr "# pkg install okular\n"

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:536
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# cd /usr/ports/graphics/okular\n"
"# make install clean\n"
msgstr ""
"# cd /usr/ports/graphics/okular\n"
"# make install clean\n"

