msgid "Gnumeric"
msgstr "Gnumeric"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:602
msgid ""
"Gnumeric is a spreadsheet program developed by the GNOME community.  It features convenient automatic guessing of user input according to the cell format with an "
"autofill system for many sequences.  It can import files in a number of popular formats, including Excel, Lotus 1-2-3, and Quattro Pro.  It has a large number of "
"built-in functions and allows all of the usual cell formats such as number, currency, date, time, and much more."
msgstr ""
"Gnumeric 是一个由 GNOME 社区开发的电子表格程序，特点是方便地根据单元格格式自动猜测用户的输入，并且自动填充。它可以导入一些常用的文件格式，包括 Excel 、 Lotus 1-2-3 "
"和 Quatto Pro。它有大量的内置功能，并允许所有的常用单元格格式，如数字、货币、日期、时间等。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/desktop/_index.adoc:604
msgid "To install Gnumeric as a package:"
msgstr "欲通过 package 来安装 Gnumeric，请执行："

